This is a clean-room implementation written against the public Motorola
M68000 Programmer's Reference Manual and the public Atari Jaguar Tom &
Jerry Technical Reference Manual. No source code from Virtual Jaguar,
MAME (Musashi), BigPEmu, or any other emulator was consulted or copied.
